t prove this. For $1\\le s\\le 50$ and $s\\le m\\le 60$ we have obtained\n$f(m,s)$ for all but 20 values.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 7 Sep 2017 21:04:42 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Sat, 28 Oct 2017 21:41:41 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Fri, 9 Mar 2018 16:20:12 GMT"},{"version":"v4","created":"Mon, 12 Mar 2018 16:05:48 GMT"},{"version":"v5","created":"Tue, 13 Mar 2018 14:14:26 GMT"},{"version":"v6","created":"Sat, 13 Jul 2019 00:40:07 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-07-16"}
