ntact durations, inter-contact times and,\nnumber of pairwise contacts. How to decide SWIM parameters using real contact\ntraces are being addressed.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 7 Sep 2017 22:19:07 GMT"}],"update_date":"2017-09-11"}
