 of the change\nin $\\delta$. The combined effect of the variation in $\\delta$ and\nacceleration/cooling of electrons is probably responsible for the observed\ndiversity of the polarization variations in the flares.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 8 Sep 2017 03:51:24 GMT"}],"update_date":"2017-12-20"}
