d, their directions. Experiments with a KUKA\nLWR4+ show that our method can successfully reproduce motions which require\ntaking advantage of the environment.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 8 Sep 2017 08:47:06 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 23 Nov 2017 07:46:47 GMT"}],"update_date":"2018-09-03"}
