_{\\rm orb}$ is\ngoverned by the intraband excitations, the Korringa relation does not hold in\nthe Dirac electron systems.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 8 Sep 2017 09:50:35 GMT"}],"update_date":"2017-09-11"}
