ation in the\ninfrared dark cloud suggest that it is a starless core located in a turbulent\nmedium with turbulence induced by Herbig-Haro jets and associated outflows.\nMore data is needed to fully understand the physical and chemical properties of\nNH$_3-$S and if/how its evolution is affected by nearby jets.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 8 Sep 2017 14:38:42 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 3 Oct 2017 14:21:59 GMT"}],"update_date":"2017-11-15"}
